description: <p>This is another of my old fonts used \
  to make inscriptions on stone. I created the MedievalSharp \
  font in around 1995 like my other fonts - when I \
  started doing the inscriptions on stone professionally. \
  It's based on gothic letters. Initially the font \
  contained only capitals and digits, and later I made \
  missing small fonts and some basical signs. In 2010 \
  I started convert my typeface designs into digital fonts. \
  The first was NovaCut and all the Nova family, \
  and here's another...</p>


